OL,3,CFootball player banned from driving
OL,4,Cafter breaking a motorcyclist's leg
OL,6,FFormer Manchester United footballer
OL,7,FNicky Butt has been banned from
OL,8,Fdriving for a year after breaking a
OL,9,Fmotorcyclist's leg in a road crash.
OL,11,FButt, 49, was driving his #100,000
OL,12,FRange Rover while heading home from
OL,13,Ftaking his son to football training in
OL,14,FBurnley.
OL,16,FIn a "momentary lapse of
OL,17,Fconcentration" he pulled out in front
OL,18,Fof a Honda motorbike ridden by Adam
OL,19,FFielding, 28, on 17 October 2022,
OL,20,FBlackburn Magistrates' Court heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
