OL,6,FMr Fielding spent two weeks in
OL,7,Fhospital after the crash recovering
OL,8,Ffrom a broken left leg and other
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,FHe has had to have metal rods inserted
OL,12,Fin his leg and has since lost his job.
OL,13,FMr. Fielding has also suffered
OL,14,Fpsychological damage and is in
OL,15,Fconstant pain, the court heard.
OL,17,FThe former midfielder has been banned
OL,18,Ffrom driving for 12 months and ordered
OL,19,Fto do 100 hours of unpaid work.
