OL,6,FButt told the court in a statement: "I
OL,7,Fcould not be more sorry."
OL,9,FButt, of Bowdon, Greater Manchester,
OL,10,Fwho admitted causing serious injury by
OL,11,Fcareless driving at an earlier
OL,12,Fhearing, was also ordered to pay a
OL,13,F#140 government surcharge and #85
OL,14,Fcosts.
OL,16,FJohn Dye, the barrister representing
OL,17,FButt, read a letter from the ex-Old
OL,18,FTrafford favourite and England
OL,19,Finternational, to Mr Fielding.
