OL,6,FIt said: "I have not stopped thinking
OL,7,Fabout the accident and the effect it
OL,8,Fmust have had on you and your family.
OL,9,FI am truly sorry about the accident.
OL,11,F"I never set out to hurt anybody that
OL,12,Fnight. What happened was a total
OL,13,Faccident. I checked and checked and
OL,14,Fchecked again.
OL,16,F"If I could go back and change the
OL,17,Fevents of that journey I would.
