OL,6,F"I hope you can put this accident
OL,7,Fbehind you. I could not be more sorry.
OL,8,FI can only hope you can take this
OL,9,Fletter for what it is, heartfelt."
OL,11,FMr Dye said Butt had stayed at the
OL,12,Fscene after the crash, had no previous
OL,13,Fconvictions and had pleaded guilty.
OL,15,FHe said Butt already does voluntary
OL,16,Fwork with released prisoners and
OL,17,Fpassed on "glowing" references, not
OL,18,Fread out in court, to the judge.
