OL,6,FHe asked for a fine for the defendant,
OL,7,Fsaying him taking part in unpaid work
OL,8,Fas part of a community order would be
OL,9,Fa "distraction" for others on the
OL,10,Fcourse and create difficulties for the
OL,11,FProbation Service.
OL,13,FBut District Judge Alex Preston said
OL,14,FButt should not be treated differently
OL,15,Fto defendants.
OL,17,FShe told Butt: "I have no doubt you
OL,18,Fdeeply regret what happened and feel
OL,19,Fgenuine remorse.
