OL,6,F"I do feel the case is serious enough
OL,7,Ffor a community order. It is a matter
OL,8,Ffor Probation how a community order is
OL,9,Fmanaged.
OL,11,F"It doesn't seem to me you should be
OL,12,Ftreated as an exceptional case because
OL,13,Fof your means.
OL,15,F"You have been unable to explain why
OL,16,Fyou did not see the victim on his
OL,17,Fmotorbike. You should not have pulled
OL,18,Fout at this junction.
OL,20,F"This was a serious error by you. All
OL,21,Fdrivers must 'Think bike' at junctions.
