OL,6,F"It is accepted by all parties however
OL,7,Fthat this chain of events was set in
OL,8,Fmotion by a momentary lapse of
OL,9,Fconcentration by you."
OL,11,FScott Parker, prosecuting, read a
OL,12,Fvictim statement from Mr Fielding in
OL,13,Fwhich he said he has lost his job as a
OL,14,FScrewfix supervisor after the
OL,15,Faccident, he was unable to do
OL,16,F"physical" work, and the crash had
OL,17,Fleft him a "dark place".
