OL,6,FMr Fielding said he now suffers from
OL,7,Fdepression, anxiety and post traumatic
OL,8,Fstress disorder (PTSD), it had
OL,9,Faffected his independence, his
OL,10,Frelationship with his girlfriend, who
OL,11,Fbecame his "carer", he had lost his
OL,12,Fsocial life and he will have to live
OL,13,Ffor the rest of his life with metal
OL,14,Frods in his left leg.
OL,16,FMr Fielding said he is now addicted to
OL,17,Fpainkillers and is in constant pain.
OL,19,FHe added: "The accident has had a
OL,20,Fsignificant impact on all areas of my
OL,21,Flife.
