OL,6,F"I have had almost two years of
OL,7,Fconstant pain and I am likely to be in
OL,8,Fpain for the rest of my life, and I am
OL,9,Funable to do things I used to enjoy.
OL,11,F"I feel like I am spending my life
OL,12,Fplanning around the pain and what I am
OL,13,Fphysically able to do."
OL,15,FButt starred in United's famed "Class
OL,16,Fof 92" with David Beckham, Ryan Giggs,
OL,17,FPaul Scholes and Gary and Phil Neville.
