OL,6,FButt helped United win six Premier
OL,7,FLeague titles, three FA Cups and a
OL,8,FChampions League trophy by the time he
OL,9,Fleft the club in 2004.
OL,11,FThe 49-year-old also signed for
OL,12,FNewcastle United, Birmingham City and
OL,13,Fshort stint in China before retiring
OL,14,Ffrom football and returning to United
OL,15,Fas a coach.
OL,17,FHe joined Giggs, Scholes and the
OL,18,FNevilles in buying Salford City FC in
OL,19,F2014.
